The father of the family in a comfortable chair sips beer and watches football. A first-grader daughter runs in: - Dad, dad, well, dad .. - Leave me alone, don't interfere! - Dad, daddy .. - Leave me alone, I said, I'm busy! TV - what is dad doing? He becomes interested in the game and after a couple of minutes he pesters his father again: - Dad, what is it - this one in black - puts a flash drive in his mouth all the time? Father, without taking his eyes off the screen: - He whistles. Daughter with surprise: - Flash drive ? Whistle??? Here is a gadget!